<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>欢迎使用 Litefs</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>欢迎使用 Litefs</h1>
            <p>一个轻量级的 Python Web 框架</p>
        </header>
        
        <main>
            <section class="features">
                <h2>特性</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>轻量级，高性能</li>
                    <li>支持 WSGI 协议</li>
                    <li>内置中间件系统</li>
                    <li>支持模板引擎</li>
                    <li>配置管理灵活</li>
                    <li>健康检查支持</li>
                </ul>
            </section>
            
            <section class="quick-start">
                <h2>快速开始</h2>
                <p>编辑 <code>app.py</code> 文件来添加你的路由和处理函数</p>
                <pre><code>@app.route("/hello")
def hello(request):
    return "Hello, World!"</code></pre>
            </section>
            
            <section class="links">
                <h2>相关链接</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/health">健康检查</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/leafcoder/litefs">GitHub 仓库</a></li>
                    <li><a href="https://github.com/leafcoder/litefs#readme">文档</a></li>
                </ul>
            </section>
        </main>
        
        <footer>
            <p>&copy; 2026 Litefs. Powered by Litefs Framework</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
